@startuml CircleGuard - Quality gates en el pipeline (HU-08)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  BorderColor #555555
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam DefaultFontName "Segoe UI"
title CircleGuard - Cadena de gates bloqueantes por pipeline (HU-08)

actor Dev as dev
actor Ops as ops

rectangle "Jenkinsfile.dev / stage / master" as pipeline {
  rectangle "1. Unit + Integration tests\n(JUnit5 + Testcontainers)" as t1
  rectangle "2. JaCoCo coverage\n(0.8.11, gate >=80% linea)" as t2
  rectangle "3. SonarQube\nwithSonarQubeEnv\n+ waitForQualityGate\nabortPipeline: true" as t3
  rectangle "4. Build JARs\n(./gradlew bootJar)" as b1
  rectangle "5. Kaniko build + push\n--customPlatform=linux/arm64" as b2
  rectangle "6. Trivy image scan\n--severity CRITICAL,HIGH\n--exit-code 1" as s1
  rectangle "7. Semver tag\n(solo master)\nbump-and-tag.sh + git push" as s2
  rectangle "8. Manual approval\n(solo master)\ninput message" as s3
  rectangle "9. Deploy a K8s\n(kubectl set image)" as d1
  rectangle "10. E2E + Performance\nrun-e2e.sh / locust" as t4
  rectangle "11. OWASP ZAP baseline\n(solo stage)\nfail en rule FAIL" as s4

  t1 -down-> t2
  t2 -down-> t3
  t3 -down-> b1
  b1 -down-> b2
  b2 -down-> s1
  s1 -down-> s2
  s2 -down-> s3
  s3 -down-> d1
  d1 -down-> t4
  t4 -down-> s4
}

rectangle "post { failure }\nslackSend(#ci-alerts)\n+ emailext(developers/culprits)" as notify_fail #FFE0E0
rectangle "post { success }\nslackSend(#ci-alerts)" as notify_ok #E0FFE0

t1 -right-> notify_fail : test fail
t3 -right-> notify_fail : quality gate fail
s1 -right-> notify_fail : CVE CRITICAL/HIGH
s4 -right-> notify_fail : ZAP rule FAIL
s4 -down-> notify_ok : pipeline ok

dev -down-> pipeline : push a feature/*
ops -right-> s3 : aprueba release vN.M.P

note bottom of pipeline
  Cada bloque bloqueante:
  - Para dev:    1, 2, 3, 6                       (sin stages 7, 11)
  - Para stage:  1, 2, 3, 6,           9, 10, 11  (sin 7, 8)
  - Para master: 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10          (sin 11)
end note

note right of notify_fail
  Mensaje incluye:
  - job, build number, rama
  - enlace a la consola
  Plugin Slack ignora si el webhook
  no esta configurado: dev local
  funciona sin Slack arriba.
end note

@enduml
